  - Life-Love=Love=Via Amoris
By: Peter Sterry
---
The Lord Jesus hath his Concubines, his Queenes, his Virgines; Saints in
Remoter Formes, Saints in higher Formes, Saints unmarried to any Forme, who
keep themselves single for the immediate imbraces of their Love.
